    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chef Gecko</strong> is a cosy riverside cooking game. Cook and deliver pizzas to the boats waiting at the drive-thru. Quick deliveries will earn you more coins. Use your profits to unlock cute new pizza toppings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras/254f47dcd65b087838b97a3f0e4d9024.avif?t=1732095093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras_big/254f47dcd65b087838b97a3f0e4d9024.avif?t=1732095093 width=800 height=328 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ORDER UP!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Chef Gecko cares about fresh food, good quality ingredients and happy customers. Head to the drive-thru and read the pizza order. Remember it! There's no time to write it down. Get the pizza to the customer before they get impatient and leave. The quicker they get their order, the more money you earn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras/09159ae5c41a1734d303a026dda0a5e2.avif?t=1732095093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras_big/09159ae5c41a1734d303a026dda0a5e2.avif?t=1732095093 width=800 height=328 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>DONT FORGET THE SAUCE!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Start with making the pizza dough. Match the arrows with your keyboard or controller to control the appliances in the kitchen. Gather the toppings the customer ordered and get chopping. Combine the order on the prep table and get it in the oven quick!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras/5f93e3ee78625672e47c7d52e0614165.avif?t=1732095093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras_big/5f93e3ee78625672e47c7d52e0614165.avif?t=1732095093 width=800 height=328 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HOLD INTERACT TO UNLOCK NEW INGREDIENTS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Put those profits to good use and unlock more pizza toppings. Delivering more complex orders equals more coins. yEy!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras/e3a3af65128a924700e51ec68b876b02.avif?t=1732095093\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3306080/extras_big/e3a3af65128a924700e51ec68b876b02.avif?t=1732095093 width=800 height=328 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NAP TIME!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There's also a bed upstairs if you need a break.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
